  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that there was not enough solidarity and indignation among the people around me to come and join me and lend a helping hand.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's part of my--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came forward because-- I, I, I can think of, of three reasons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would say that the, the catalyst-- because I have actually not joined, so far, into survive-- with other people to testify.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have not joined the, the, the Hidden Children Movement and so forth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I hadn't heard or seen a situation whereby the-- this ironic twist being maltreated so badly, that's redundant, being maltreated by the people who are supposed to hide us from the oppressor.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that having one of your oppressors be so kind to you, that twist I hadn't heard and seen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I, I, I had, I had difficulty with talking about these people who, after all, did save our lives.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I thought that an initiative like Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Spielberg's to-- for the record-- to immortalize what happened, I think deserves the support of anyone who has anything to contribute, because he's actually writing history as factually as it can be written by first-hand testimony from people, and not, and not, the kind of revisionism that is written by most-- most histories are-- of most historic episode.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Plus, the fact that I wanted to, at least, be on-- have on the record that not all the people that hid Jewish children were nice people, did it out of the goodness of their hearts, that some of them could be-- could do it for, for pecuniary reasons, for the advantage of improving, for the money, for a better standard of living.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it could be still sadistic and bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
